title: The Mysterious Strangers 002 (2013) (Digital) (Nahga-Empire).cbr
description: The mysterious organization O.C.C.U.L.T. plans to harness the power of the temple, which could prove catastrophic for the rest of the world. Unfortunately, Michael and Verity have been captured, and their ally Sandoval has turned against them! Their only hope may lie with the temple itself - if only they can uncover its secrets before O.C.C.U.L.T. does!
